    <line rend="center">Asia.</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e2-0044.03"/>
    <line>From all the blasts of Heaven thou hast descended&#8212;</line>
    <line>Yes like a spirit, like a thought which makes</line>
    <line>Unwonted tears throng to the horny eyes</line>
    <line>And beatings haunt the desolated heart</line>
    <line>Which should have learnt repose&#8212;thou hast descended</line>
    <line>Cradled in tempests thou dost wake o Spring</line>
    <line>O child of many winds.. <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">a</del>
        <add place="intralinear">A</add>
      </mod>s suddenly</line>
    <line>Thou comest as the memory of a dream</line>
    <line>Which now is sad because it hath been sweet;</line>
    <line>Like genius o<mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">f</del>
        <add place="intralinear">r</add>
      </mod> like joy which riseth up</line>
    <line>As from the Earth clothing with golden clouds</line>
    <line>The desart of our life....</line>
    <line>This is the season this the day the hour,</line>
    <line>At sunrise thou shouldst come sweet sister mine ...</line>
    <line>Too long<del rend="strikethrough">-</del>desired too long delaying come . ..</line>
